21
00:01:28,958 --> 00:01:29,583
Puman...

22
00:01:29,583 --> 00:01:30,416
Yaman.

23
00:01:34,916 --> 00:01:36,333
The two of them are...

24
00:01:36,791 --> 00:01:38,666
