47
00:02:41,583 --> 00:02:43,166
I like the way you smile.

48
00:02:51,041 --> 00:02:51,958
Do you want to take a photo?

49
00:03:00,166 --> 00:03:01,291
1, 2, 3.

50
00:03:09,291 --> 00:03:10,458
1, 2, 3.

51
00:03:14,708 --> 00:03:15,458
