132
00:08:18,208 --> 00:08:19,458
It's okay.

133
00:08:19,458 --> 00:08:20,916
That is your work.

134
00:08:21,041 --> 00:08:21,916
I can understand.

135
00:08:29,791 --> 00:08:30,708
Miss Meilin.

136
00:08:33,791 --> 00:08:35,166
