142
00:08:48,041 --> 00:08:50,458
Aren't we here to be happy?

143
00:08:53,666 --> 00:08:54,291
Smile.

144
00:08:58,833 --> 00:08:59,833
Smile.

145
00:09:02,000 --> 00:09:02,416
Great.

146
00:09:08,708 --> 00:09:09,541
So,

147
00:09:09,541 --> 00:09:11,208
