181
00:10:52,666 --> 00:10:53,666
Of course.

182
00:10:54,416 --> 00:10:55,333
Okay.

183
00:11:07,583 --> 00:11:08,416
You first.

184
00:11:51,541 --> 00:11:52,291
Meilin

185
00:11:52,791 --> 00:11:53,166
Yeah?

186
00:11:54,166 --> 00:11:55,083
